GLOWTAGLIST_DESCRIPTION: Shows the players list of Glow tags
NO_TAGS: {{author}} You don't have a **Glow** tag yet. You can create them with the command: `{{prefix}}gtc <Name> <Emoji>`
GLOWTAGLIST_EXTRA_INFO: Using this command without a prompt will show your Glow tag list, adding another player's username or user id will show their Glow tag list. You can use the "{{prefix}}glowtagcreate" command in order to create more tags
